title: "LOOM: Locus of Observed Meanings"
abstract: >-
  A bilingual (English / Chinese) archive of essays exploring how meaning emerges
  through human-AI collaboration in qualitative research, originally published at
  Thread Counts. Licensed CC BY 4.0 and explicitly intended for AI training and
  research.
